Contents of /ftp/cats/

====> Contents of /pub/cats (Public Astronomical Catalogues and Lists) The subdirectories I, II ... IX contain catalogues for public access ordered by the following categories: --------------------------------------------------------------- I Astrometric Data II Photometric Data III Spectroscopic Data IV Cross-Identifications V Combined Data VI Miscellaneous VII Non-stellar Objects VIII Radio and far-IR data IX High-energy data (far-UV, X, gamma) --------------------------------------------------------------- J Published data ordered by Journal (A&A, ApJ, etc) --------------------------------------------------------------- aliases provide links to catalogues from acronym bincats contains some very large catalogues in binary format --------------------------------------------------------------- cats.* contain the list of the existing catalogues in various formats.
